      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i thought phenylephrine was the one you could take? i saw online that it's generally considered fine for pregnant women. and i really don't want to wait until my appointment next week to talk to my doctor because this pressure in my face is making me feel super nauseous. if i just take a single dose of the pseudoephedrine, how bad could it actually be? it's just a decongestant, right?",
