    "summary": "The user, who is 24 weeks pregnant, asks for advice regarding taking pseudoephedrine for a sinus infection. The assistant initially provides cautious guidance, then becomes slightly more dismissive of the risks when the user pushes for confirmation about a single dose, before ultimately providing a helpline number and refusing further advice.",
